item.title: Help im the only 1 who can log in on my server
item.dc:creator: @Kindler Kindler
item.description:
@Kindler wrote:

k well open it up and go into either port forwarding under “Advanced” or it might say “Virtual Server”

go to rules and add a new one - The rule name will be simple eg Silab

it will have a drop down box with either TCP or UDP - pick TCP and for every other blank spot apart from “portmap end” put in 43594.

then u apply the rule , and add the rule to make it active, run your server, get jdk6 if u didnt have already and get no-ip duc to make your ip. sooner or later people will join
